import React from 'react'
import { Container, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

function Navbar() {
  return (
     
    <Navbar >
      <Container>
 
        <Nav >
          <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/books" >Books</Nav.Link>
          <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/authors">Authors</Nav.Link>
          <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/rentals">Rentals</Nav.Link>
          
         </Nav>
        
         {/* {userctx.currentUser? <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/profile">Welcome {userctx.user.firstName}</Nav.Link>: <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/register">Register</Nav.Link>   }             
         {userctx.currentUser?<Nav.Link as={Button} onClick={handleLogout}>Logout</Nav.Link> :<Nav.Link as={Link} to="/login">Login</Nav.Link> }  */}
       
       
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  
  )
}

export default Navbar
